graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|OAuth auth| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    Dashboard -->|Routes, ConsoleLinks| OpenShift
    Dashboard -->|resource mgmt| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 22+]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6]
    Dashboard -->|backend framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient[kubernetes/client-node]
    Dashboard -->|auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|component status| Operator[ODH/RHODS Operator]
    Dashboard -->|notebook mgmt| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|model serving| KServe[KServe]
    Dashboard -->|model registry| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Dashboard -->|pipeline mgmt| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    Dashboard -->|feature stores| Feast[Feast Operator]
    Dashboard -->|distributed workloads| Ray[Ray Operator]
    Dashboard -->|NIM integration| NIM[NVIDIA NIM]
    Dashboard -->|metrics queries| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    ServiceMesh[Service Mesh] -.->|optional sidecars| Dashboard
    Gateway[Gateway API] -.->|HTTPRoute ingress| Dashboard
    Dashboard -.->|federated UI| ModelRegistryUI[Model Registry UI]
    Dashboard -.->|federated UI| GenAIUI[GenAI UI]
    Dashboard -.->|federated UI| MaaSUI[MaaS UI]

    %% External Services
    Dashboard -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage]
    Dashboard -->|container images| ImageRegistry[Image Registries]

